data.title: StartLine Racing
data.meta_site_name: StartLine Racing - Your Best Race Starts Here
data.text:
Thank you for running with StartLine Racing. We strive for 100% accurate timing, every time! If you have a problem with your results please let us know and we will do everything we can to correct any potential errors.

If you placed in the top three in your age group (CONGRATULATIONS!!) in one of our StartLine Racing owned or managed events but were not able to stay for the awards ceremony you can still get your placement award. Please go to our SLR Online Store here to pay for the shipping and handling and we will mail you award directly to you!
